\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Australia Fuel Supply Dashboard \'97 Analysis & Build Brief\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 Purpose\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Build a consumer-facing website that helps everyday Australians understand the current fuel crisis by showing 
\f0\b where we stand now
\f1\b0  and 
\f0\b why
\f1\b0  \'97 tracing the supply chain from the Strait of Hormuz through Asian refineries to the bowser at a local servo.\
The audience is the general public. The tone should be calm, factual, and explanatory \'97 not alarmist, but not sugar-coating either. Think of it as "the dashboard a good journalist would build."\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

