\f0\b connected story
\f1\b0 , not just show isolated numbers. The mental model is a 
\f0\b supply chain flowing left to right
\f1\b0 , from global source 
\f2 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  regional processing 
\f2 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  domestic stock 
\f2 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  retail availability.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

